00:38:51.230 --> 00:38:52.950
And one of the
reasons for that is

00:38:52.950 --> 00:38:55.700
that many of the countries
that were very much part

00:38:55.700 --> 00:38:59.100
of the debate now have problems
of too little population

00:38:59.100 --> 00:38:59.820
growth.

00:38:59.820 --> 00:39:02.360
And so there's a number
of rich countries now

00:39:02.360 --> 00:39:06.140
that are deeply troubled
by declining populations.

00:39:06.140 --> 00:39:08.170
And if there's one
thing more difficult,

00:39:08.170 --> 00:39:10.840
if your an economic manager
of a country, one thing

00:39:10.840 --> 00:39:13.250
more difficult than a very
